#    - Set OPENAI_API_KEY above
#    - Cost: ~$0.15 per 1000 reviews with gpt-4o-mini
#
#    Option B: Google Gemini (FREE!)
#    --------------------------------
#    - Get API key: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
#    - Set GEMINI_API_KEY above
#    - FREE: 1500 requests/day with gemini-1.5-flash-latest
#    - No credit card required!
#
#    Option C: Local Models (FREE, Private)
#    ---------------------------------------
#    - Install Ollama: https://ollama.ai
#    - Run: ollama pull qwen2.5-coder:7b
#    - Run: ollama serve
#    - Select "qwen2.5-coder:7b (local)" in the UI
#    - No API key needed, runs offline!
#
# 3. Start Development:
#    npm run dev
